Buster's Bistro

Start Section 2
About us
Since 2013 Buster’s Sanford has been providing the ultimate European experience laced with tradition and a touch of contemporary flare. We feature an exotic mix of the world's most exquisite beers, top quality food, and innovative cocktails. Our frites are hand cut from fresh peeled russet potatoes and double fried with pride to give you the taste of the world’s best fry, an international food which originated from Europe.
Buster's Sanford is located in the heart of the thriving and vibrant Historic Downtown Sanford area. Buster's has weekly Trivia, Live Music, Karaoke, Live DJ and much more. Buster's opens at 11am daily with a daily late night kitchen until Midnight 7 nights a week and has fantastic nightlife until 2am on weekends serving great beers, cocktails, shots and everything else you could want.
Buster's is owned by Robbie Kennerney from Dublin, Ireland where he brings his knowledge and experience of the European bar and restaurant scene and helps create an ambiance like no other in Sanford. Buster's is a perfect venue for parties, receptions, get togethers, catered events and has one of Sanford's best daily Happy Hours Monday-Friday from 3-6pm where a variety of items are available for just $5.
We hope to see you here at Buster's Sanford soon!
End Section 2
Start Section 4 Custom section
We do our best to make a difference in the community hosting extravagant beer pairing dinners in collaboration with the most renowned chefs in the state to donate the proceeds to charities ranging from local theaters to nation-wide charities aiding in the fight against disease. Keep in touch with our events page and social media outlets to help us in these ventures. It is our hope that you will visit and see what we take pride in and become one of our friends and a part of our family.
Buster's is also a spot for the community to come together, not only do we offer phenomenal drink and fare, Buster's is the spot for major events in Historic Downtown Sanford. We hold weekly events such as Trivia on Tuesday, Live Music on Friday, and a live DJ every Saturday night. There are also reoccurring monthly events such as Paint Night hosted by local artist Nick Criscitelli, the Brew Club of Seminole County meetings every first Thursday.  Don't forget to mark your calendars for our yearly charity events for charities like Save the Chimps and Audubon Center for Birds of Prey and of course our Annual Belgian Independence Day on July 21st.
Buster's is the perfect spot for whatever occasion you are looking to go out for. Looking to take a night off from your busy life, come relax and unwind at Buster's while we cook the perfect meal for you and provide a delicious beer to quench your thirst. Date night? Enjoy our relaxing, secluded beer garden in the back while you toast under the lights. Want to grab a few beers with your friends and catch your favorite soccer team in action? Stop by and see the games featured on our big screen TVs, from Orlando City, Orlando Pride, and all the European teams in between, we've got you covered!
There's always something to do at Buster's! A new beer to try, and special dish or mixed drink featured just for that day, or if you just want the perfect spot to catch up with the ones your love! Stop by any day of the week, excluding Mondays when we're closed, and we'll be happy to serve you the Belgian experience of a lifetime right here in Central Florida. We look forward to seeing you at our restaurant! Sante!

Every Friday
Karaoke is now at Buster’s every Friday AND Saturday night from 10pm in downtown Sanford!  Come join us and enjoy some great late night specials and sing your heart out with your friends
10:00 PM - 02:00 AM
Saturday Bottomless Brunch
Saturday August 30th
Sunday may 8th
Every Saturday
Our famous brunch at Buster's is now available Saturday as well as Sunday!!
From 8am-3pm enjoy Sanford's best brunch with bottomless mimosas, Bloody Mary's and THC infused Blood Mary's available for just $20 with the purchase of an entree.
For reservations:
https://www.busterssanford.com/reservations
We'll hope to see you all here on Saturday AND Sunday!
08:00 AM - 03:00 PM
Drag Brunch - 8/30
Saturday August 30th
Sunday may 8th
Join us here at Buster's in Sanford for our weekly Drag 'Tree' Brunch event every Saturday at 1pm hosted by MysTree Hugga.
This promises to be a really fun event with a full brunch menu, bottomless mimosas and some great entertainment.
Reservations are recommended but not required.
https://busterssanford.com/reservations
Any questions please feel free to let us know! We'll hope to see you all here!!
